name: o_god_the_mail_07
description:
O god, did I forget to read my mail again? This one looks important - these numbers look important - I can't deal with that right now though. I'll just leave it here and think about it. I'll think about it all the time until I have a moment to serve what's in it - to serve it like a god. O god, the mail.

Part 7 of a series begun on knownorigin.io
